data.description: Welcome to this timeless & tastefully upgraded 5 bedroom+  3 full & 1 half bath home! Conveniently located on a Cul-De-Sac block, zoned to the highly sought after Klein ISD schools and minutes away from shopping, restaurants, and entertainment. The homes upgrades include new flooring throughout, completely re-envisioned baths throughout, updated light fixtures, upgraded ceiling fans, & beautiful granite countertop throughout kitchen+ backsplash supplement the upgraded, top tier appliances that are installed. Upstairs find a theater room for relaxation. Completing this home are recently added solar window screens on the front of the home, custom wood blinds installed throughout, a smart home refrigerator. Too many upgrades to list. Contact agent for more details!
